                "s2_paper_id": "d0672936a9abd01e81b0b5cbc92083d0d3fe23df",
                "title": "SPELLING RULES FOR THE MONSTER/SEMPLE TOWER.",
                "year": 2014,
                "venue": "",
                "citation_count": 1,
                "reference_count": 13,
                "abstract": "We further study the incidence relations that arise from the various subtow- ers, known as Baby Monsters, which exist within the R 3 -Monster Tower. This allows us to complete the RV T class spelling rules. We also present a method of calculating the various Baby Monsters that appear within the Monster Tower.",
